---
title: Saucy Beef Stir-Fry with Ginger-Green Rice
description: Traditional beef stir-fry is excellent, but this garlic and ginger concoction is seriously mind-blowing! This dish is the perfect flavour and texture combination of tender meat, crispy veggies, and satisfying rice.
